25/* This header file holds function prototypes and data types that are
26 * internal to the drm (not exported to user space) but shared across
27 * drivers and platforms */
28
29#ifndef __DRM_INTERNAL_H__
30#define __DRM_INTERNAL_H__
31
32/**
33 * Drawable information.
34 */
35struct drm_drawable_info {
36 unsigned int num_rects;
37 struct drm_clip_rect *rects;
38};
39
40#endif
